title: North Carolina doctor sues over abortion pill access, in test case on federal power
description: An abortion provider is suing North Carolina over its restrictions on the abortion pill, in what's expected to become a test case with potential nationwide implications.
author: Anne Flaherty

title: NC Democrat calls hit-and-run in state-issued vehicle a 'serious mistake,' refuses to resign
description: North Carolina State Auditor Beth Wood, who has been charged in a hit-and-run incident on Dec. 8 in Raleigh, has issued an apology while Republicans are urging her to resign.
author: Greg Norman
